cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with automatic speech recognition (ASR) and language modeling techniques for code-switching speech.
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on ASR for low-resourced acoustic data.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses neural network-based language models for rescoring.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with developing an end-to-end ASR pipeline for code-switching speech.
- cs.SI (Speech and Audio Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with ASR for speech data.
